   "end": "5.480", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.600", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine sehr verehrten Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.560", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr uns war nicht zu jedem Zeitpunkt nachvollziehbar, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.280", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was damals in Frankfurt passiert ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.480", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn ich einen Strich darunter ziehe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.360", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "komme ich zu dem Schluss: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.960", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich jedenfalls w\u00fcrde Herrn Glaser mein Geld trotzdem nicht anvertrauen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.360", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber das sei anheimgestellt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.680", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Kollege Ernst, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.320", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Verm\u00f6gensteuer ist eine verdammt teure Steuer, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.640", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und zwar vor allen Dingen f\u00fcr den Staat. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.280", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Etwa ein Drittel der Einnahmen gehen am Ende des Tages f\u00fcr Verwaltungskosten drauf. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.680", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das hei\u00dft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.120", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es ist eine Steuer, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.880", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die nicht besonders leicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.280", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern besonders kompliziert und besonders teuer f\u00fcr den Staat zu erheben ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.880", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist \u00fcbrigens ein Grund daf\u00fcr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.800", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "warum in den letzten 20\u00a0Jahren in zahlreichen Staaten der Europ\u00e4ischen Union die Verm\u00f6gensteuer abgeschafft worden ist\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.160", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "anders, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.320", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "als Sie hier versucht haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.800", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das zu suggerieren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.640", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich will auf den Aspekt Ihres Antrages zu sprechen kommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.800", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den ich pers\u00f6nlich f\u00fcr den spannendsten halte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.960", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "n\u00e4mlich auf den Vorschlag, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.400", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
