   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.280", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das m\u00f6chte ich kurz durchdeklinieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "70.040", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Zentrum f\u00fcr Europ\u00e4ische Wirtschaftsforschung in Mannheim hat dankenswerterweise ausgerechnet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "70.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.560", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was eine Verm\u00f6gensteuer in H\u00f6he von 5\u00a0Prozent bedeuten w\u00fcrde und wie hoch die Ertragsteuer, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.360", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "beispielsweise die K\u00f6rperschaftsteuer, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.200", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sein m\u00fcsste, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.560", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
