   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.200", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das w\u00e4re relativ hoch in diesen Niedrigzinsphasen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.720", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bei niedrigerem Zins m\u00fcsste der Steuersatz noch h\u00f6her sein\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "103.400", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "m\u00fcsste die K\u00f6rperschaftsteuer 193,04\u00a0Prozent betragen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "103.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.120", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Kollegen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.560", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man k\u00f6nnte jetzt meinen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "110.760", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Linkspartei einem untergegangenen sozialistischen System nacheifert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "110.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "111.400", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mitnichten; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "111.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.920", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn 193,04\u00a0Prozent sind mehr als das Doppelte des damaligen Spitzensteuersatzes der K\u00f6rperschaftsteuer in der Deutschen Demokratischen Republik, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.920", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
